**New:**
```rust
pub struct SubtypeRelation {
    pub sub_ty: Ty,
    pub super_ty: Ty,
}
```

Also update line 1485 in PredicateKind enum:
- Change: `SubType(SubtypePredicate),`
- To: `SubType(SubtypeRelation),`

